text: William McIntyre (10 April 1877 - 18 April 1943) was an Australian cricketer. He played four first-class matches for New South Wales between 1905/06 and 1906/07. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1877 births Category:1943 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
title: William McIntyre (Australian cricketer)
